    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The edible, soft, berry-like fruit of the plant Rubus fruticosus and its varieties. It is botanically a compound fruit consisting of many small, typically dark purple, drupelets on a conical receptacle from which the ripe fruit is easily detached.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
